OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ministers are facing calls to prevent  
OL,6, leaseholders being threatened with     
OL,7, losing their home over unpaid charges. 
OL,9,FUnder current laws, branded "draconian"
OL,10,Fby campaigners, a property can be      
OL,11,Frepossessed if the leaseholder owes as 
OL,12,Flittle as #350.                        
OL,14,FThere is cross-party support for       
OL,15,Fscrapping the practice of forfeiture in
OL,16,Fthe Leasehold Reform Bill, which       
OL,17,Freturns to the Lords on Wednesday.     
OL,19,FThe government says it recognises the  
OL,20,Fissue needs to be tackled.             
